description:
In case you have tried to install Windows Live Movie Maker 2012 today, you may have enountered an error during installation with the error code 0x800c0006. This error code means that the wlsetup-all.exe file doesn't contain the MUI (Multilingual User Interface) files for the display language your computer is using. To fix this, you need to temporarly change your display language to English. This video shows you how to do that.
